title: Temple of the Undead King
story: The temple of the Undead King is situated deep in the frozen lands, protected by the dangerous local fauna and harsh weather. Currently it is overrun with owls, which don't care about the history of the place. It is said that the temple is rich with treasures of gold and maps and charts.

notes.text: A dying druid, gems among his belongings.
A blood-stained sword in a strongbox.
A notable wooden door on the eastern wall of the large chamber.
A fresco on the wall, totally destroyed by hobgoblin vandals.
A torch and some gold tucked under some debris.
